WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'XCenter' is a Workbench game where the story goes like this:
you find yourself on an island located in the center of a lake and
you want to go to the shore, that is, on the border of the lake.
To succeed, you have to click on various islands (including the
central island) that appear randomly on the lake, this cause some
other islands to appear or disappear. To complete the game, there
must be an uninterrupted series of islands lined-up horizontally
or vertically from the center to one of the border tiles. Try to
complete the game in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

